
## 7. فایل .gitignore

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.log

# Buildozer
.buildozer/
bin/
*.apk
*.aab

# Virtual Environment
venv/
env/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Kivy
*.kv

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Downloads
downloads/
*.mp4
*.mp3
*.bin

# History
history.json

# Local
local.properties
